Convert string to stringfish vector

Source: R/stringfish.R
sf_convert.Rd

Convert string to stringfish vector

Usage

sf_convert(x)

Arguments

x

<character> vector

Value

<character> stringfish vector

Examples

sf_convert(random_hcpcs(50))
